uai, CGT's union delegate for Sade, the company that employed Dioumassy.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 1031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 964, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Confederation_of_Labour_of_the_Argentines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4307140981914605e-27, \"text\": \"CGT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Confederation_of_Labour_of_the_Argentines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Confederation_of_Labour_of_the_Argentines\"}, {\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 993, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marquis_de_Sade\", \"score\": 0.9999999999417923, \"rank\": 5.809660286636465e-11, \"text\": \"Sade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marquis_de_Sade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marquis_de_Sade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this mobilisation\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"our brother\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"comrade\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"colleague\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyes Chouai\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"Dioumassy\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were serious safety issues.\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1067, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"serious safety issues\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1066}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were no signs for pedestrian crossings, no traffic flow, the trucks did not have a beep sound when backing up, even though there was poor visibility.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1223, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no signs\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"pedestrian crossings\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1112}, {\"ngram\": \"no traffic flow\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"the trucks\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"a beep sound\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1167}, {\"ngram\": \"poor visibility\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1222}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no one directing the trucks,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1240}, {\"ngram\": \"the trucks\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chouai visited the site after the tragedy.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chouai\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"the tragedy\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I met a young man who told me that Amara was one of the first people to arrive on site on the morning of June 16.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1433, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1355, \"end\": 1360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amarah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.597712359747777e-32, \"text\": \"Amara\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amarah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amarah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a young man\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"the first people\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"site\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1406}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had bought a bag of pastries and distributed them to all the workers, encouraging them to take more than one,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bag\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"pastries\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"all the workers\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Amara's coworker had tears in his eyes when he told me this story.\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1559, \"end\": 1564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amarah\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.597712359747777e-32, \"text\": \"Amara\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amarah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amarah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"his eyes\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1597}, {\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 1614, \"to\": 1624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Amara was someone who always smiled and was kind and generous to people he worked with and his friends.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Amara\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"his friends\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was a force of nature, but his face always had kindness and he always looked after people.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a force\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"nature\", \"from\": 1748, \"to\": 1754}, {\"ngram\": \"his face\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"kindness\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 1822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His family also told me he was always the person who his brothers and sisters confided in, who moderated family discussions and looked after everyone in Mali.\\\"\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1983, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1977, \"end\": 1981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mali\", \"score\": 0.99999448399624, \"rank\": 5.5160342141026875e-06, \"text\": \"Mali\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mali\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His family\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1834}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 1