 2483, \"end\": 2488, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.904014593364388e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The city\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2460}, {\"ngram\": \"open-water swimming and triathlon events\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2590}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because of the Olympics, there were deadlines to meet for certain construction sites, such as this one, which had the goal to make the Seine more swimmable for the Olympics and the events that will take place.\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2745, \"end\": 2750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.904014593364388e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"deadlines\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2655}, {\"ngram\": \"certain construction sites\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"this one\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2712}, {\"ngram\": \"the goal\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2732}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2813, \"to\": 2818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were deadlines, stress, pressure on workers,\\\" Lyes said.\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"deadlines\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2848}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2858}, {\"ngram\": \"workers\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyes\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2876}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of the city's grand projects for the games, such as those to clean up the Seine, come with labour costs.\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2993, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2963, \"end\": 2968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999922693, \"rank\": 7.904014593364388e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city's grand projects\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2917}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2931}, {\"ngram\": \"labour costs\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Infrastructure projects are contracted out to large construction companies with varying degrees of labour code enforcement.\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3118, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Infrastructure projects\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"large construction companies\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3069}, {\"ngram\": \"varying degrees\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"labour code enforcement\", \"from\": 3094, \"to\": 3117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There have been at least 181 workplace accidents, including 31 serious accidents, on construction projects related to the Olympics, according to Nicolas Ferrand, director of SOLIDEO - a publicly-funded firm established to build the permanent facilities that will remain after the event.\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"at least 181 workplace accidents\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"31 serious accidents\", \"from\": 3179, \"to\": 3199}, {\"ngram\": \"construction projects\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3225}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3237, \"to\": 3249}, {\"ngram\": \"Nicolas Ferrand\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3279}, {\"ngram\": \"director\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"SOLIDEO\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3300}, {\"ngram\": \"a publicly-funded firm\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3325}, {\"ngram\": \"the permanent facilities\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3371}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Accidents and workers' rights violations are not unique to Olympics construction, but there is pressure to complete everything by the hard deadlines set for the games, and safety can start to slip through the cracks.\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Accidents\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3416}, {\"ngram\": \"workers' rights violations\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3447}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics construction\", \"from\": 3466, \"to\": 3487}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3510}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3533}, {\"ngram\": \"the hard deadlines\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 3564, \"to\": 3573}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 3579, \"to\": 3585}, {\"ngram\": \"the cracks\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is a trend that Jules Boykoff, researcher and author of the book Power Games: A Political History of the Olympics, has observed throughout multiple venues, including London and Rio de Janeiro.\", \"from\": 3625, \"to\": 3822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3646, \"end\": 3659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Boykoff\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jules Boykoff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Boykoff\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jules_Boykoff\"}, {\"begin\": 3796, \"end\": 3802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999979851183816, \"rank\": 2.014885434274441e-06, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 3807, \"end\": 3821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4929867342245635e-17, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a trend\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3640}, {\"ngram\": \"researcher\", \"from\": 3661, \"to\": 3671}, {\"ngram\": \"author\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3682}, {\"ngram\": \"the book\", \"from\": 3686, \"to\": 3694}, {\"ngram\": \"Power Games\", \"from\": 3695, \"to\": 3706}, {\"ngram\": \"A Political History\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3727}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3743}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple venues\", \"from\": 3769, \"to\": 3784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When it comes to the city, the Olympics often acts like a parasite and puts all these different demands on cities, including the deadlines that the Olympics automatically bring,\\\" Boykoff told Al Jazeera.\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 4028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4017, \"end\": 4027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.516588193725011e-13, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 3842, \"to\": 3850}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3864}, {\"ngram\": \"a parasite\", \"from\": 3881, \"to\": 3891}, {\"ngram\": \"all these different demands\", \"from\": 3901, \"to\": 3928}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 3932, \"to\": 3938}, {\"ngram\": \"the deadlines\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 3963}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 3981}, {\"ngram\": \"Boykoff\", \"from\": 4004, \"to\": 4011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you have deadlines, like to build the Olympic Village, for example, all sorts of possibilities around corruption that kick into motion - all sorts of possibilities around worker exploitation to meet those external deadlines by that parasitic organisation, the IOC [International Olympic Committee].\\\"\", \"from\": 4030, \"to\": 4335, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4074, \"end\": 4089, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6830896665767257e-16, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 4301, \"end\": 4332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"deadlines\", \"from\": 4045, \"to\": 4054}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 4095, \"to\": 4102}, {\"ngram\": \"possibilities\", \"from\": 4117, \"to\": 4130}, {\"ngram\": \"corruption\", \"from\": 4138, \"to\": 4148}, {\"ngram\": \"motion\", \"from\": 4164, \"to\": 4170}, {\"ngram\": \"all sorts\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4182}, {\"ngram\": \"possibilities\", \"from\": 4186, \"to\": 4199}, {\"ngram\": \"worker exploitation\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4226}, {\"ngram\": \"those external deadlines\", \"from\": 4235, \"to\": 4259}, {\"ngram\": \"that parasitic organisation\", \"from\": 4263, \"to\": 4290}, {\"ngram\": \"the IOC\", \"from\": 4292, \"to\": 4299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Prior to the games, Paris 2024 Organising Committee and its partners established a \\\"social charter\\\" with social, economic and environmental goals, signed by trade unions and employer organisations on June 19, 2019.\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4357, \"end\": 4367, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4274981206928148e-28, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 4346, \"to\": 4355}, {\"ngram\": \"its partners\", \"from\": 4393, \"to\": 4405}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"social charter\", \"from\": 4418, \"to\": 4435}, {\"ngram\": \"social, economic and environmental goals\", \"from\": 4442, \"to\": 4482}, {\"ngram\": \"trade unions\", \"from\": 4494, \"to\": 4506}, {\"ngram\": \"employer organisations\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4533}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 4537, \"to\": 4541}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The charter promised to \\\"fight against illegal labour, anti\\u2011competitive practices, and discrimination, and will monitor working conditions and limit unstable employment\\\".\", \"from\": 4553, \"to\": 4723, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The charter\", \"from\": 4553, \"to\": 4564}, {\"ngram\": \"illegal labour\", \"from\": 4592, \"to\": 4606}, {\"ngram\": \"anti\\u2011competitive practices\", \"from\": 4608, \"to\": 4634}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 4640, \"to\": 4654}, {\"ngram\": \"working conditions\", \"from\": 4673, \"to\": 4691}, {\"ngram\": \"unstable employment\", \"from\": 4702, \"to\": 4721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympic Charter, in spite of everything, has made it possible to reduce the danger of construction sites.\", \"from\": 4725, \"to\": 4835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic Charter\", \"from\": 4726, \"to\": 4745}, {\"ngram\": \"spite\", \"from\": 4750, \"to\": 4755}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4759, \"to\": 4769}, {\"ngram\": \"the danger\", \"from\": 4802, \"to\": 4812}, {\"ngram\": \"construction sites\", \"from\": 4816, \"to\": 4834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To have better traceability, even if everything is not perfect,\\\" Gerard Re, confederal secretary of the CGT in charge of the rights of migrant workers, told Al Jazeera.\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 5004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4901, \"end\": 4907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barksdale_Organization\", \"score\": 0.9999999983365342, \"rank\": 1.5723748269103957e-09, \"text\": \"Gerard\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barksdale_Organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Barksdale_Organization\"}, {\"begin\": 4940, \"end\": 4943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Confederation_of_Labour_of_the_Argentines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4307140981914605e-27, \"text\": \"CGT\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Confederation_of_Labour_of_the_Argentines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Confederation_of_Labour_of_the_Argentines\"}, {\"begin\": 4993, \"end\": 5003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.516588193725011e-13, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"better traceability\", \"from\": 4844, \"to\": 4863}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4883}, {\"ngram\": \"confederal secretary\", \"from\": 4912, \"to\": 4932}, {\"ngram\": \"charge\", \"from\": 4947, \"to\": 4953}, {\"ngram\": \"the rights\", \"from\": 4957, \"to\": 4967}, {\"ngram\": \"migrant workers\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 4986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With multiple subcontracting companies, inevitably, some of them worked with undocumented workers.\", \"from\": 5006, \"to\": 5105, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multiple subcontracting companies\", \"from\": 5012, \"to\": 5045}, {\"ngram\": \"undocumented workers\", \"from\": 5084, \"to\": 5104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, the fact that we had this charter and an organising committee with diverse representatives helped mitigate the possible effects.\\\"\", \"from\": 5106, \"to\": 5249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 5120, \"to\": 5128}, {\"ngram\": \"this charter\", \"from\": 5141, \"to\": 5153}, {\"ngram\": \"an organising committee\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5181}, {\"ngram\": \"diverse representatives\", \"from\": 5187, \"to\": 5210}, {\"ngram\": \"the possible effects\", \"from\": 5227, \"to\": 5247}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As part of the charter, much of the construction for Olympic venues is directed SOLIDEO.\", \"from\": 5250, \"to\": 5338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 5253, \"to\": 5257}, {\"ngram\": \"the charter\", \"from\": 5261, \"to\": 5272}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction\", \"from\": 5282, \"to\": 5298}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic venues\", \"from\": 5303, \"to\": 5317}, {\"ngram\": \"SOLIDEO\", \"from\": 5330, \"to\": 5337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Bassin d'Austerlitz project was not, however, part of this group.\", \"from\": 5339, \"to\": 5408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Bassin d'Austerlitz project\", \"from\": 5339, \"to\": 5370}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 5389, \"to\": 5393}, {\"ngram\": \"this group\", \"from\": 5397, \"to\": 5407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On SOLIDEO projects, there were more regulations, respect for work,\\\" Re said.\", \"from\": 5410, \"to\": 5488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SOLIDEO projects\", \"from\": 5414, \"to\": 5430}, {\"ngram\": \"more regulations\", \"from\": 5443, \"to\": 5459}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 5461, \"to\": 5468}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 5473, \"to\": 5477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In France, where more than two workers are killed on average every day on construction sites according to the most recent report from France's national health insurance system, the added pressure exacerbated ongoing challenges.\", \"from\": 5490, \"to\": 5717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5493, \"end\": 5499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9265406018676873, \"rank\": 0.07917470912123707, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 5624, \"end\": 5630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9265406018676873, \"rank\": 0.07917470912123707, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than two workers\", \"from\": 5507, \"to\": 5528}, {\"ngram\": \"construction sites\", \"from\": 5564, \"to\": 5582}, {\"ngram\": \"the most recent report\", \"from\": 5596, \"to\": 5618}, {\"ngram\": \"the added pressure\", \"from\": 5667, \"to\": 5685}, {\"ngram\": \"ongoing challenges\", \"from\": 5698, \"to\": 5716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics tend to magnify social issues and social problems that already exist in society,\\\" Boykoff said.\", \"from\": 5719, \"to\": 5828, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 5720, \"to\": 5732}, {\"ngram\": \"social issues\", \"from\": 5749, \"to\": 5762}, {\"ngram\": \"social problems\", \"from\": 5767, \"to\": 5782}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 5805, \"to\": 5812}, {\"ngram\": \"Boykoff\", \"from\": 5815, \"to\": 5822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a clear track record, a clear Olympic trend where Olympic host cities enlist the assistance of undocumented labour, and because undocumented labour has so little leverage in society, they often, unfortunately, get exploited through these relations.\\\"\", \"from\": 5829, \"to\": 6088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a clear track record\", \"from\": 5839, \"to\": 5859}, {\"ngram\": \"a clear Olympic trend\", \"from\": 5861, \"to\": 5882}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic host cities\", \"from\": 5889, \"to\": 5908}, {\"ngram\": \"the assistance\", \"from\": 5916, \"to\": 5930}, {\"ngram\": \"undocumented labour\", \"from\": 5934, \"to\": 5953}, {\"ngram\": \"undocumented labour\", \"from\": 5967, \"to\": 5986}, {\"ngram\": \"so little leverage\", \"from\": 5991, \"to\": 6009}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 6013, \"to\": 6020}, {\"ngram\": \"these relations\", \"from\": 6071, \"to\": 6086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France ranks as the fourth deadliest country in Europe for workers and has more reported workplace accidents than any other member of the European Union, with 560,000 incidents in 2022, said the health insurance report.\", \"from\": 6090, \"to\": 6309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6090, \"end\": 6096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9265406018676873, \"rank\": 0.07917470912123707, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 6237, \"end\": 6242, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8584044799083634e-14, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fourth deadliest country\", \"from\": 6106, \"to\": 6134}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 6138, \"to\": 6144}, {\"ngram\": \"workers\", \"from\": 6149, \"to\": 6156}, {\"ngram\": \"more reported workplace accidents\", \"from\": 6165, \"to\": 6198}, {\"ngram\": \"any other member\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6220}, {\"ngram\": \"560,000 incidents\", \"from\": 6249, \"to\": 6266}, {\"ngram\": \"the health insurance report\", \"from\": 6281, \"to\": 6308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For many years now in France, public services have been slashed, and labour inspectors are no exception.\", \"from\": 6311, \"to\": 6416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6334, \"end\": 6340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9265406018676873, \"rank\": 0.07917470912123707, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many years\", \"from\": 6316, \"to\": 6326}, {\"ngram\": \"public services\", \"from\": 6342, \"to\": 6357}, {\"ngram\": \"labour inspectors\", \"from\": 6381, \"to\": 6398}, {\"ngram\": \"no exception\", \"from\": 6403, \"to\": 6415}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, we are sorely lacking enough labour inspectors to enable us to check that companies are complying with the rules for working conditions.\", \"from\": 6417, \"to\": 6566, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a result\", \"from\": 6420, \"to\": 6428}, {\"ngram\": \"enough labour inspectors\", \"from\": 6452, \"to\": 6476}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 6487, \"to\": 6489}, {\"ngram\": \"companies\", \"from\": 6504, \"to\": 6513}, {\"ngram\": \"the rules\", \"from\": 6533, \"to\": 6542}, {\"ngram\": \"working conditions\", \"from\": 6547, \"to\": 6565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In terms of legislation, we are also lacking-in particular on undocumented workers,\\\" said Re.\", \"from\": 6567, \"to\": 6660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 6570, \"to\": 6575}, {\"ngram\": \"legislation\", \"from\": 6579, \"to\": 6590}, {\"ngram\": \"undocumented workers\", \"from\": 6629, \"to\": 6649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added that in France, 50 to 60 percent of workers in the construction sector are immigrants, with many undocumented.\", \"from\": 6662, \"to\": 6781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6679, \"end\": 6685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9265406018676873, \"rank\": 0.07917470912123707, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"50 to 60 percent\", \"from\": 6687, \"to\": 6703}, {\"ngram\": \"workers\", \"from\": 6707, \"to\": 6714}, {\"ngram\": \"the construction sector\", \"from\": 6718, \"to\": 6741}, {\"ngram\": \"immigrants\", \"from\": 6746, \"to\": 6756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In October 2023, more than 500 undocumented workers from 33 companies involved in construction projects for the games went on strike, refusing to return to work until they received proper immigration documents and the legal right to work in France.\", \"from\": 6783, \"to\": 7031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7024, \"end\": 7030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9265406018676873, \"rank\": 0.07917470912123707, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 6786, \"to\": 6793}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 500 undocumented workers\", \"from\": 6800, \"to\": 6834}, {\"ngram\": \"33 companies\", \"from\": 6840, \"to\": 6852}, {\"ngram\": \"construction projects\", \"from\": 6865, \"to\": 6886}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 6891, \"to\": 6900}, {\"ngram\": \"strike\", \"from\": 6909, \"to\": 6915}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 6939, \"to\": 6943}, {\"ngram\": \"proper immigration documents\", \"from\": 6964, \"to\": 6992}, {\"ngram\": \"the legal right\", \"from\": 6997, \"to\": 7012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They gathered at the construction site at Arena de la Chapelle and threatened to occupy additional Olympics venues.\", \"from\": 7032, \"to\": 7147, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7080, \"end\": 7094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/De_La_Chapelle\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"de la Chapelle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/De_La_Chapelle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/De_La_Chapelle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the construction site\", \"from\": 7049, \"to\": 7070}, {\"ngram\": \"additional Olympics venues\", \"from\": 7120, \"to\": 7146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After negotiations, they successfully legalised their migration status.\", \"from\": 7148, \"to\": 7219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"negotiations\", \"from\": 7154, \"to\": 7166}, {\"ngram\": \"their migration status\", \"from\": 7196, \"to\": 7218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"France's strong history of organised labour does help push for some changes, such as the Olympic Charter.\", \"from\": 7221, \"to\": 7326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7221, \"end\": 7227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9265406018676873, \"rank\": 0.07917470912123707, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"organised labour\", \"from\": 7248, \"to\": 7264}, {\"ngram\": \"some changes\", \"from\": 7284, \"to\": 7296}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Charter\", \"from\": 7306, \"to\": 7325}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Paris, what's definitely stood out to me is the power of unions, and how they have really made it a point to use the Olympics as a source of leverage,\\\" Boykoff said.\", \"from\": 7328, \"to\": 7497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7332, \"end\": 7337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.821764988839331e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the power\", \"from\"